snippet: Giancarlo Stanton hit a three-run homer in the first inning that bounced on the roof of Miami's clubhouse beyond the left-field wall during the Marlins' 8-1 win over the Houston Astros on Tuesday....

headline.print_headline: Stanton Hits Long Homer; Marlins Beat Astros 8-1
headline.main: Stanton Hits Long Homer; Marlins Beat Astros 8-1

lead_paragraph: Giancarlo Stanton hit a three-run homer in the first inning that bounced on the roof of Miami's clubhouse beyond the left-field wall during the Marlins' 8-1 win over the Houston Astros on Tuesday.
